TI  - Optimized ridge-furrow technology with biochar amendment for alfalfa yield enhancement and soil erosion reduction based on a structural equation model on sloping land
T2  - AGRICULTURAL WATER MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Soil moisture
KW  - Sediment
KW  - Soil nutrient loss
