TI  - Olive groves around the lake. A ten-thousand-year history of a Cretan landscape (Greece) reveals the dominant role of humans in making this Mediterranean ecosystem
T2  - QUATERNARY SCIENCE REVIEWS
LA  - English
KW  - Paleoecology
