TI  - Examining the disparities: A cross-sectional study of socio-economic factors and food insecurity in Togo
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - SECURITY
KW  - DETERMINANTS
KW  - OUTCOMES
