FX  - We extend our deep appreciation to the communities of Air Pinang, Kuala Baru, Kuala Makmur, Pulau Siumat, Pulau Bengkalak, Sambay, and Ujung Tinggi. Their invaluable citizen science data within the PiSiSi MPA area significantly contributed to our research. We also thank the representatives of the 26 villages within the PiSiSi MPA, along with all stakeholders who actively participated, provided vital input, and supported our public consultation events and zoning plan mapping stages. Our gratitude extends to the dedicated students from Syiah Kuala University's Ocean Diving Club for their crucial role in collecting coral reef resilience data in six subdistricts. We acknowledge funding support from The Arcadia Fund and The Darwin Initiative, pivotal in executing this study successfully.
