TI  - Quantification of ecosystem services from mangrove silvofishery
T2  - GLOBAL JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND MANAGEMENT-GJESM
LA  - English
KW  - Carbon storage
KW  - Climate regulation
