TI  - Analyzing land use land cover (LULC) changes induced by the run-of river project and respondent survey: a case of Ghazi Barotha Hydropower Project on Indus River, Pakistan
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH COMMUNICATIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Indus River
