TI  - Seasonal Spatial Distribution of Metapenaeopsis provocatoria longirostris in the Southern Yellow and East China Seas and Habitat Area Variation Prediction Under Climate Scenarios
T2  - BIOLOGY-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - East Asia
