TI  - Supplemental irrigation using brackish water on maize in tropical semi-arid regions of Brazil: yield and economic analysis
T2  - SCIENTIA AGRICOLA
LA  - English
KW  - rainfed farming
KW  - salinity
KW  - supplementary irrigation
KW  - biosaline agriculture
KW  - SALINE WATER
KW  - MANAGEMENT STRATEGIES
KW  - CONJUNCTIVE USE
