TI  - Synchronous spatio-temporal changes in potential habitats of Trachurus murphyi and Dosidicus gigas off Chile in relation to regime shift of Pacific decadal oscillation
T2  - JOURNAL OF MARINE SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Trachurus murphyi
