TI  - Hydroponic farming hotspot analysis using the Getis-Ord Gi* statistic and high-resolution satellite data of Majuli Island, India
T2  - REMOTE SENSING LETTERS
LA  - English
KW  - SPATIAL AUTOCORRELATION
KW  - ASSOCIATION
KW  - EXPANSION
