TI  - Constraints and capacities for novel livelihood adaptation: lessons from agricultural adoption in an African dryland pastoralist system
T2  - REGIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Diversification
KW  - Pastoralism
