TI  - Intercrop overyielding is maintained under estimated water and nitrogen stress in maize-cowpea on-farm trials in semi-arid Zimbabwe
T2  - FIELD CROPS RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Soil-crop modeling
KW  - STICS
KW  - Nitrogen fixation
