TI  - Research Paper Thermal conversion of fish bones into fertilizers and biostimulants for plant growth-A low tech valorization process for the development of circular economy in least developed countries
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL CHEMICAL ENGINEERING
