TI  - Narrowing maize yield gaps across smallholder farming systems in Zambia: what interventions, where, and for whom?
T2  - AGRONOMY FOR SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Food security
KW  - Sustainable intensification
