TI  - Diversity in young shark habitats provides the potential for portfolio effects
T2  - MARINE ECOLOGY PROGRESS SERIES
LA  - English
KW  - Shark
KW  - Nursery
KW  - Portfolio effect
KW  - Population sustainability
KW  - Elasmobranch
