TI  - Based on the Spatial Multi-Scale Habitat Model, the Response of Habitat Suitability of Purpleback Flying Squid (Sthenoteuthis oualaniensis) to Sea Surface Temperature Variations in the Nansha Offshore Area, South China Sea
