TI  - Drought-tolerant rice, weather index insurance, and comprehensive risk management for smallholders: evidence from a multi-year field experiment in India
T2  - AUSTRALIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL AND RESOURCE ECONOMICS
LA  - English
KW  - agriculture
KW  - drought tolerance
KW  - index insurance
KW  - India
