TI  - Prioritizing options for multi-objective agricultural development through the Positive Deviance approach
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-SMART AGRICULTURE
KW  - SUSTAINABLE INTENSIFICATION
KW  - SYSTEMS
KW  - FOOD
KW  - AFRICA
